'''Budy''' {{IPA-pl|[|'|b|u|d|y|]}} is a [[village]] in the administrative district of [[Gmina Fa<U+0142>k<U+00F3>w]], within [[Ko<U+0144>skie County]], [[<U+015A>wi<U+0119>tokrzyskie Voivodeship]], in south-central [[Poland]]. It lies approximately {{convert|7|km|mi|0}} south of [[Fa<U+0142>k<U+00F3>w]], {{convert|27|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} south-west of [[Ko<U+0144>skie]], and {{convert|43|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north-west of the regional capital [[Kielce]].<ref name="TERYT">{{cite web |url=http://www.stat.gov.pl/broker/access/prefile/listPreFiles.jspa |title=Central Statistical Office (GUS) - TERYT (National Register of Territorial Land Apportionment Journal) |date=2008-06-01 |language=Polish}}</ref>

The village has a population of 190.

